# Keys for the DEDICATED Supabase TEST project (ref: kqbppawdvnjuxpvrshee).
# Used by DB-touching integration tests (test-plan §3 Phase 2+). NEVER reuse prod keys.
# Copy this file to .env.test (git-ignored) and fill in real values from the test project's
# panel: Settings -> API.

# base project URL only — https://<ref>.supabase.co (NOT the .../rest/v1/ REST URL)
SUPABASE_URL=###
# anon / publishable key (RLS-enforced client)
SUPABASE_KEY=###
# service-role key — full-privilege, bypasses RLS; required for DB read-back and account-deletion (Phase 4)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=###
